Multifunctional Use: You will get 6pack clear hard pen organizers. This organizer box is perfect to be used for school, office or at home for organizing pens, marker, carryon, art, craft and other school supply.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love the Pencil boxes.
reviews.reviewText: I love different pencils, and pens, and markers etc. These containers work perfectly and fit all my items. Perfect size and I like how the lids clip on the ends. I will definitely be buying some more. They help keep me organized also.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Way to Organize
reviews.reviewText: Bought a few sets of these to organize our craft supplies. They took awhile to get here, but they all arrived in good condition. I love them, keeps everything in one spot and easy to get to. I would definitely buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars The measurements pictured are NOT the interior measurements!
reviews.reviewText: I'm very disappointed in the size of the boxes. The exterior measures 8 1/8" (handle to handle) by 5 1/2" while the interior measures 7 1/4" by 4 7/8". The interior will not hold a full-length pencil without it being placed at an angle! How can it be called a "pencil box" if it doesn't hold a full-length pencil?!!I've taken my review from a 1 star to a 4 star for two reasons. First, I see that the interior measurements have been added within the text of the product description. Second, the seller provided excellent customer service by offering a full refund.

reviews.reviewText: My kids have a lot of crayons, pens, markers and color pencils. This came in handy and are great because you can stack them.The kids are able to open them with out having to get you over and over again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The lids attach to the box very well, so it’s pretty sealable. The description says “extra large”, but they’re not. I’d say large size at the MOST. I was luckily able to barely fit all of my alcohol markers in these.The boxes do attach, but it’s by the handles, and you have to have the lids off of the boxes in order to do this. You just have a bunch of loose lids and it’s kind of annoying. I had to put them under my tower.
